Actions.Text: REFERRED TO MENTAL HEALTH AND DEVELOPMENTAL DISABILITIES

Title: Makes available information regarding the process for individuals to obtain eligibility for services offered by the office for people with developmental disabilities
Summary: Instructs the commissioner of the office for people with developmental disabilities to make available on the office website, information regarding the process for individuals to obtain eligibility for services and to seek access to services.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to making available information regarding the process for individuals to obtain eligibility for services offered by the office for people with developmental disabilities
